		<title>Surrounding Charlotte cities prepare to help handle DNC protesters</title>
		<link>http://theppl.us/blog/965</link>
		<comments>http://theppl.us/blog/965#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 15 Jun 2012 17:56:01 +0000</pubDate>
